wdi2-NE.CON.TOTL.KD.def: Final consumption expenditure (formerly total consumption) is the sum of household final consumption expenditure (formerly private consumption) and general government final consumption expenditure (formerly general government consumption). Data are in constant 2010 U.S. dollars.
wdi2-NE.CON.TOTL.KD.name: Final consumption expenditure
wdi2-NE.CON.TOTL.KD.source: World Bank national accounts data, and OECD National Accounts data files.
